{"tid":972483,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Huh] Devil May Cry 4 Nero Perfect Kill 無傷","createTime":"2019-01-07T11:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T14:33:43.000Z","uid":105546,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1964b2d62ae5abc147c54adfd7087d7f780e02d","tid":972483,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"相隔大半月再開post 今次係Devil May Cry 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我拍左Nero無傷打大佬 劇情佢總共有7個boss<br />\n暫時只係打左5隻 仲係度攻略緊點樣無傷殺Dante <br />\nBTW新年第一個post所以先同大家講句新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=y0DhchcOK0k&amp;list=PL4g-9LQx2owci9&ndash;NW9m-XZdqOguy2HXh&amp;index=2&amp;t=18s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy0DhchcOK0k%26list%3DPL4g-9LQx2owci9%E2%80%93NW9m-XZdqOguy2HXh%26index%3D2%26t%3D18s&d=E%2F%2B5pn%2FqAz4%2Bd1X9LuAQF54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f0e6a159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=y0DhchcOK0k&amp;list=PL4g-9LQx2owci9&ndash;NW9m-XZdqOguy2HXh&amp;index=2&amp;t=18s</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係更多嘅簡介:<br />\nDMC4總共有三個難度 我只係選左第二個 同最高難度嘅分別係中途嘅怪仔數量 而大佬就好硬正 無得打到咁上下可以整野好型嘅重擊 而招式就無分別 <br />\n雖然每條片都係約5分鐘 但都用左好多心機㗎 因為佢無得直接打大佬 所以每次都要走前邊嘅劇情 但我一唔小心殺左個大佬就要重新嚟過 走一次前戲都係平均5分鐘 但好傷心機<br />\n而每隻大佬都有佢自己嘅血量分佈 即係每隻都係10格血 但可以重擊 變攻擊模式 發癲嘅時間都唔一樣 所以要揾曬出嚟先 之後再攻略點避同攻擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攻擊都唔可以貪多 因為佢地有時佢地會硬食反擊 我就會無空間閃避 但後退同時又可以撳實正方形Charged Shot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以你地會發現點解隻隻boss都係無傷 唯有第三隻蛇妖係一傷 因為我難得拍到一次無傷之後發現無拍底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嬲撚到仆街 跟住第二次就一傷 所以就算尻數唔撚理咁up左佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果想係下面負評嘅巴絲希望可以講埋點解唔鐘意嚟比我改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再subscribe睇住我改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37c1d453986c8bd7b34cc09755c27c13a4b060c","tid":972483,"uid":5883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"加油比心機"},{"pid":"3d6054b3385dd6b99eb9f19e3b4243c92e6e2781","tid":972483,"uid":105546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b37c1d453986c8bd7b34cc09755c27c13a4b060c","tid":972483,"uid":5883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"加油比心機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f260905e84462bda3f7587e60a1d87d63eb121","tid":972483,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:33:29.000Z","msg":"Dmc4係爽快既"},{"pid":"ad956b4a415847b7da521b85a5ab2d6a74005f41","tid":972483,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f260905e84462bda3f7587e60a1d87d63eb121","tid":972483,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:33:29.000Z","msg":"Dmc4係爽快既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"3月又有DMC5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以幾拍到幾分鐘一條 啲重擊又型 仲叫有少少難度 <br />\n應該好符合大家要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc0533a75d5067a9ea4cfcbfe9366c47e056c35","tid":972483,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"a048150411f95dd5bf9eb50b73e2d01ab844f7d2","tid":972483,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"07431a4fa4e56ab68bcfd4b81452efdc568b3714","tid":972483,"uid":5883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"20cae3410b037ca4a7a8ff4ef9c79711b36ae312","tid":972483,"uid":588